WEBVTT

00:06:28.450 --> 00:06:31.061
"Tomorrow morning,
the bus is going to come in.

00:06:31.085 --> 00:06:32.807
If you believe in me,

00:06:32.831 --> 00:06:34.896
if you believe in me,

00:06:34.920 --> 00:06:40.457
you will wake me up
and take me to the bus station.

00:06:40.838 --> 00:06:43.220
If you don't, I'll understand."

00:06:43.244 --> 00:06:44.895
Then I went to sleep.

00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:50.212
The next morning, my father
was standing beside me

00:06:50.236 --> 00:06:52.472
to take me to the bus stop.

00:06:52.496 --> 00:06:56.871
(Applause)

00:06:56.895 --> 00:07:00.960
That day, I understood
the importance of words.